> 301 views, 512 likes. :/﻿

In order to counter view spam bots, YouTube counts views up to 301 before releasing the restriction when the views are verified. Likes and dislikes, on the other hand, do not need to be verified because they are linked with accounts. I can watch a video multiple times, but I can only like it once.

